usage:

python generate_plot_optimalP.py 10 $phenotype $genelist $network $chrpos $phenotype $boost
10 = number of shuffles
$phenotype = outputfile name
$genelist = input genes (for validation)
$network = network (download file from http://www.inetbio.org/aranet/downloadnetwork.php)
$chrpos = snp chromosome position file (FT22_chr.pos) //gns.txt
$phenotype = name of the phenotype (ex. FT:flowering time) //input
$boost = snp-pvalue file for boosting(7_FT22_pvalue_forboost_incremental) //p-value gwas summury file --> snp & p-value mapping

example:

python generate_plot_optimalP.py 10 FT_test.out floweringVern_noIEPgenes AraNet.txt FT22_chr.pos FT 7_FT22_pvalue_forboost_incremental
